data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in a family-friendly neighborhood with excellent schools! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath 2-story residence offers the perfect blend of style, space, and functionality. Step inside and be captivated by the custom cabinets adorning the modern kitchen, a chef's delight that combines practicality with elegance.  The allure continues into the master bedroom, where a double trey ceiling adds an air of sophistication. Indulge in the luxury of the oversized vanity, complemented by a garden tub/shower for a spa-like experience. With four bedrooms in total, this home provides ample space for a growing family or visiting guests.  Entertain in the large great room, warmed by the cozy fireplace, creating an inviting ambiance for gatherings and making memories. The convenience of a spacious laundry room and a 2-car garage ensures that your daily routines are effortless and organized.  Step outside to your private oasis—a flat backyard enclosed by a privacy fence, offering a safe haven for children to play freely. Picture-perfect, the property boasts a serene creek at the back, adding a touch of nature's tranquility to your everyday life.  Situated on almost 1 acre of land, this home offers both space and serenity. The neighborhood buzzes with the laughter of children, creating a vibrant community atmosphere. Plus, benefit from the peace of mind knowing that your children will receive an excellent education from nearby top-rated schools.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this house your home. Experience the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and community in this beautiful residence. Come and see for yourself—schedule a viewing today and let your new chapter begin!
